WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Fill sample bottle to 7 ml with hot tub water.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:11.500
Add CYA Reagent to sample bottle up to 14 ml.

00:00:12.500 --> 00:00:18.000
Cap and shake sample bottle for 30 seconds.

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:24.000
Hold small tube at waste level with your back to the sun.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:29.000
Transfer cloudy solution into small tube until dot obscured.

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:36.000
Read CYA value at water level.